</style>
<p>
<p>Em 160 registros, 56 apresentam <span class="math inline">\(B\)</span> e 32 apresentam simultaneamente <span class="math inline">\(A\)</span> e <span class="math inline">\(B\)</span>. Qual é <span class="math inline">\(P(A\mid B)\)</span>?</p>
</p>]]></text>
</questiontext>
<generalfeedback format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<p><span class="math display">\[P(A\mid B)=\frac{P(A\cap B)}{P(B)}
=\frac{32}{56}=0.5714.\]</span></p>
</p>]]></text>
</generalfeedback>
